inoremap {      {}<Left>
inoremap [      []<Left>
inoremap ()     ()<Left>
inoremap {}     {}<Left>
inoremap []     []<Left>
" Lazy (plus back up for {}) 
inoremap (<space> (  )<Left><Left>
